      &lt;img alt="A white Sonos Era 100 speaker sitting on a marble kitchen countertop beside a paper towel roll and cooking utensils." src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/GVuInxxF1Tu-ljbfi3A33Hm3VdM=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73541435/DSCF0459.0.jpg" /&gt;
        &lt;figcaption&gt;&lt;em&gt;The Era 100 might resemble a roll of paper towels, but it remains our default smart speaker.&lt;/em&gt; | Photo by Chris Welch / The Verge&lt;/figcaption&gt;
    &lt;/figure&gt;

  &lt;p id="J6Zf7I"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.anrdoezrs.net/links/8532386/type/dlg/sid/verge/https://www.sonos.com/en-us/shop/promotional-offers" rel="sponsored nofollow noopener" target="_blank"&gt;Sonos’ Labor Day sale&lt;/a&gt; is bringing discounts to a variety of smart speakers and soundbars until September 2nd, many of which are on sale elsewhere for the same price. Both the &lt;strong&gt;Sonos Era 100&lt;/strong&gt; and portable &lt;strong&gt;Move 2&lt;/strong&gt; are 20 percent off, which means you can get the Era 100 from &lt;a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0BW34LCB8/?tag=theverge02-20" rel="sponsored nofollow noopener" target="_blank"&gt;Amazon&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://howl.me/cmWt7hRGy5M"&gt;Best Buy&lt;/a&gt;, and &lt;a href="https://www.anrdoezrs.net/links/8532386/type/dlg/sid/verge/https://www.sonos.com/en-us/shop/era-100" rel="sponsored nofollow noopener" target="_blank"&gt;Sonos&lt;/a&gt; for $199 ($50 off) or the Move 2 for $359 ($90 off) via the same retailers (&lt;a href="https://www.amazon.com/Sonos-Move-Wireless-Portable-Bluetooth/dp/B0CGGYYK2D/?tag=theverge02-20" rel="sponsored nofollow noopener" target="_blank"&gt;Amazon&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://howl.me/cmWt9DH9OzH"&gt;Best Buy&lt;/a&gt;, and &lt;a href="https://www.anrdoezrs.net/links/8532386/type/dlg/sid/verge/https://www.sonos.com/en-us/shop/move-2" rel="sponsored nofollow noopener" target="_blank"&gt;Sonos&lt;/a&gt;).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="c-float-left c-float-hang"&gt;&lt;aside id="f7qiKk"&gt;&lt;div data-anthem-component="readmore" data-anthem-component-data='{"stories":[{"title":"The best Sonos speakers to buy right now","url":"https://www.theverge.com/23507492/sonos-best-speaker-one-roam-move-five-arc-beam-ray-sub"},{"title":"Sonos CEO says the old app can’t be rereleased","url":"https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/20/24224754/sonos-ceo-old-s2-app-re-release-cant-be"},{"title":"This is Sonos’ next flagship soundbar","url":"https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/11/24195947/sonos-lasso-soundbar-photos-features-leak"}]}'&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/aside&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
